{
  "stem": "19518.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All right, we did not have a big apartment, so by us, no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they did take out our furniture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They came, and they took the furniture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And yes, on the 1st of December, prior to allowing-- no, that was in November of '39-- they closed off the Jewish quarters.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the looting and robbing, for 36 hours, went on endlessly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They closed off the streets, the tramways that passed through the main streets of the Jewish quarters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one had-- was allowed to get on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No one was allowed to get off in that-- passing from that area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I recall seven of them walked into our home, into our apartment, with the guns drawing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you made the wrong move, bingo, you were shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Fortunately, in-- at that time in our building, nobody-- everybody cooperated with them and whatever there was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I recall they had pillowcases, my mother's pillowcases, they took.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were throwing candlesticks, and candelabra, and whatever else that was worthwhile in silver.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they started looking for gold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They made my mother undress to remove her girdle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they stopped with that girdle, and they were going over if there is anything hidden, whether dollars are hidden there, or some jewelry.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll never forget that experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It just was a horrendous feeling, especially my poor mother, when they made her undressed, and she objected.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they said, I'm going to kill you if you don't do it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we said, and my father said, do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We knew she has nothing on her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But nonetheless, not-- nothing would have stopped them from killing her.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
